<section id="reviews" class="reviews-section">
  <div class="reviews-header">
    <h2 class="reviews-title" data-i18n="reviews.title">Ce spun oaspeții noștri</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="reviews-grid">
    <!-- Review 1 -->
    <div class="review-card">
      <div class="review-stars">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <p class="review-text" data-i18n="reviews.t1">„Am petrecut un sejur minunat la această cabană! Personalul este foarte amabil, iar locația îți oferă tot confortul necesar pentru a te bucura pe deplin de natură și liniște. O alegere excelentă!”</p>
      <div class="review-author">- Puia Andreea</div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Review 2 -->
    <div class="review-card">
      <div class="review-stars">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <p class="review-text" data-i18n="reviews.t2">„Am avut ocazia să petrecem câteva zile la Chalet Chiba, situat în Timișu de Jos, la doar 6 km de centrul orașului Brașov, și experiența a fost absolut memorabilă.”</p>
      <div class="review-author">- Alex Suteu</div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Review 3 -->
    <div class="review-card">
      <div class="review-stars">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <p class="review-text" data-i18n="reviews.t3">„Am avut o ședere minunată în această cabană frumoasă, ascunsă chiar între munți. Spațiul a fost curat, bine întreținut. Recomand cu căldură acest loc atât pentru muncă, cât și pentru odihnă.”</p>
      <div class="review-author">- Nermin Sharbek</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reviews-section {
    padding: 5rem 4.5rem; /* Reduced from 8rem */
    background: var(--off);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .reviews-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem; /* Reduced from 5rem */
  }
  
  .reviews-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--forest);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  
  .reviews-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem; /* Reduced from 3rem */
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
  }
  
  .review-card {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2.2rem 2rem; /* Reduced from 3rem 2.5rem */
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
  }
  
  .review-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }
  
  .review-stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem; /* Reduced from 1.8rem */
  }
  
  .review-stars svg {
    width: 18px; /* Reduced from 20px */
    height: 18px;
  }
  
  .review-text {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem; /* Reduced from 1.3rem */
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--forest);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }
  
  .review-author {
    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .reviews-section {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
